data.description: ***HOME PLUS A CARRIAGE HOUSE*** Welcome to 714 Tennessee St, Ringgold, GA - a charming 3-bed, 2-bath residence boasting 2,056 sqft of well-designed living space. As you step inside, be greeted by the warm ambiance of hardwood flooring and the gentle breeze of ceiling fans throughout.The heart of this home is its spacious kitchen, a culinary haven featuring ample cabinets and counter space for your culinary adventures. Natural light floods the interior through numerous windows, enhancing the open flow floorplan and creating an inviting atmosphere for gatherings.Experience the joy of indoor-outdoor living with a screened-in porch sunroom, perfect for enjoying the beauty of the surrounding 1.51-acre lot adorned with mature trees. The property also includes a convenient 2-car garage, providing shelter for your vehicles and additional storage.But that's not all - this property comes with an extra treat. A separate guest suite awaits in the back, offering a private retreat with 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom, a patio, and a kitchenette. Ideal for guests, extended family, or even as a rental opportunity.Whether you're captivated by the spacious interiors, the allure of the outdoor spaces, or the versatility of the guest suite, 714 Tennessee St is a place where comfort and convenience converge. Don't miss the chance to make this delightful property your new home. Schedule your showing today and embrace the lifestyle that awaits you in Ringgold, GA!
